Jimmy Kimmel said Piers Morgan was once “as close to a friend as Donald Trump has.” Now, the two appear to be at each other’s throats in a new teaser promoting an interview Morgan did with the former president. Although the interview hasn’t even aired yet, Morgan and Trump are already arguing about what really happened. Meanwhile, Kimmel and his crew gave the chat a makeover ― and it has a truly disturbing ending. You’ve been warned: